author: Max Mohenu For THUMP
title: Kaytranada Drops Breezy, Soulful Reworks Of TLC's "Diggin' On You" And Latrelle's "House Party"
text:
January 6, 2017 6:10 PM By Max Mohenu Share Tweet 
Photo by Chieff Bosompra 
After a prolific 2016, Kaytranada has kicked off 2017 by sharing two remixes on his SoundCloud. 
The Montreal producer recently unveiled a breezy, 2-step club edit of TLC's " Diggin' On You ," and a shimmering soul rework of R&B singer Latrelle's 2001 Neptunes-produced single " House Party ." Both tracks were featured on his most recent mixtape 0.001% , along with his extended version of Chance the Rapper's "All Night." 
Listen to both songs below.
